  "purpose": "Check DNS/domain availability (RDAP/EPP) and shepherd a member-principal acquisition via the Cloudflare-Registrar at-cost path. The charter-clean inverse of a retail registrar: no fiat inflow, no markup/affiliate, no speculation. Closes the gap between minting an actor DID and the name existing.",
